{"tid":460388,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[教學] Apple Watch 3代/ iPhone 8/ iPhone X 加入Suica 日本西瓜卡","createTime":"2017-11-06T15:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T00:58:31.000Z","uid":1826,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c6aa484977ef4d7506b04380485e688230214e","tid":460388,"uid":1826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T15:01:07.000Z","msg":"其實由今年開始, Apple Watch 3代/ iPhone 8/ iPhone X 都可以直接加Suica 西瓜卡落去.  好處係, 你唔洗再帶張Suica 卡 落地鐵.  有上面事旦一樣就dood 到.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係日本買左隻Apple Watch 3代 LTE 版.  過往係要日版iphone 或 apple watch 先可以加suica 卡.  而加你自要有以上3種其中一款就唔洗啦.  我係日本買係純粹貪佢有LTE 版.  要用香港iphone 8/X 或apple watch 3代加Suica 係好簡單.<br />\n<br />\n1.  去申請番個 JR East ID. 係方便你有咩問題都有得login 番入去攪.  <a href=\"https://my.jreast.co.jp/web/au/LoginForm.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.jreast.co.jp%2Fweb%2Fau%2FLoginForm.aspx&d=CKWVjQs%2BwpqvpYAkDhezpGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=7e53fa0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://my.jreast.co.jp/web/au/LoginForm.aspx</a>  去新規會員登錄<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img924/7010/k4g1Rd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg924%2F7010%2Fk4g1Rd.jpg&h=81153af8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/6517/IFr5RS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F6517%2FIFr5RS.jpg&h=c7da8118&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 跟住好似會收到email 叫你confirm.  <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/4118/RWahdF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F4118%2FRWahdF.jpg&h=33739f06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.  跟住填 個你起既username, password , (搵地方記低佢)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/2784/Tfc05n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F2784%2FTfc05n.jpg&h=90c9c5ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/2013/kBKmOR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F2013%2FkBKmOR.jpg&h=0a450cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img923/1315/Wwye2V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg923%2F1315%2FWwye2V.jpg&h=03fae86e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4.  下一部就係真係起張Suica 卡.  <span style=\"color: red;\">你就算電話唔係iphone 8/X, 只要你有 Apple Watch 3 代一樣可以起到張Suica 卡.</span><br />\n<br />\n首先你電話pair 左你隻Apple Watch 3 代.  跟住係iphone download Suica  個app.  <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/suica/id1156875272?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fsuica%2Fid1156875272%3Fmt%3D8&d=CKWVjQs%2BwpqvpYAkDhezpGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=fffe9abc\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/suica/id1156875272?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一開波又係要你入資料 <span style=\"color: red;\">(搵地方mark 低佢)</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/3645/0O6xDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F3645%2F0O6xDa.jpg&h=174a1287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img923/274/AyHQrc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg923%2F274%2FAyHQrc.jpg&h=6faf530b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日文姓可以用 アラガギ<br />\n日文名可以用　ユイ<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/3654/METxR9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F3654%2FMETxR9.jpg&h=46975014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住揀個問題, 自己提供個答案, 要黎唔記得password 個陣reset 用既 <span style=\"color: red;\">(搵地方mark 低佢)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img924/3423/xi1Uln.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg924%2F3423%2Fxi1Uln.jpg&h=552d31a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img924/5598/IpgaIc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg924%2F5598%2FIpgaIc.jpg&h=b1f6cff3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 開個app 就可以加卡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img923/7783/SstNSK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg923%2F7783%2FSstNSK.jpg&h=923ffcdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住揀&quot;記名式&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img923/9861/tj6wio.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg923%2F9861%2Ftj6wio.jpg&h=46c92f46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/5060/eYOf6O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F5060%2FeYOf6O.jpg&h=73040886&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最尾揀charge 1000 yen.  用apple pay 俾錢就攪掂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img924/7770/gsf363.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg924%2F7770%2Fgsf363.jpg&h=b740ed59&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最尾就會見到你有張新既 Suica 卡. 有1000 yen.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img924/3070/AtmWnc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg924%2F3070%2FAtmWnc.jpg&h=9cf80855&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"116c9e771767049acb97c916ea9fdee123733d23","tid":460388,"uid":1826,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T15:06:55.000Z","msg":"跟住就將你之前起既 JR East ID 卡, link 落去你新起既Suica 卡到.<br />\n<br />\n番去JR East ID 個度login, 用番你之前起既 login id 同password<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://my.jreast.co.jp/web/au/LoginForm.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmy.jreast.co.jp%2Fweb%2Fau%2FLoginForm.aspx&d=CKWVjQs%2BwpqvpYAkDhezpGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=7e53fa0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://my.jreast.co.jp/web/au/LoginForm.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img924/1023/VZmqHj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg924%2F1023%2FVZmqHj.jpg&h=669bef48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住連攜揀番モバイルSuica<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img922/7021/OPWxiY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg922%2F7021%2FOPWxiY.jpg&h=35ffc1f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你剛剛申請Suica 卡個陣入左 email 同 password 架嘛.  你link 落去個陣會用呢個黎將佢link 落去你個JR East ID 度."},{"pid":"ab0e9f51de0d3ef05ba6b60f4ff221795c0247a0","tid":460388,"uid":1826,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T15:15:09.000Z","msg":"如果你換手機之類, 你係一定要reset 左你隻apple watch 先會俾你再pair 過.  你reset 個陣佢會warn 你, 你係咪有方法再入得番你張suica 卡, 否則卡入面d 錢會無晒.  呢個就係點解開波個陣要你開個 JR East ID, link 落你張suica 卡到.  有咩事都仲入得番個JR East ID.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當你真係要換手機, 你要reset 隻apple watch.  你首先要係iphone 個Setting &gt; General &gt; Language &amp; Region 個度, 轉做日本. 因為轉左先可以係手機既wallet 加到suica 卡.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你reset 完隻apple watch.  會乜都無晒.  去 <a href=\"https://www.mobilesuica.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mobilesuica.com%2F&d=CKWVjQs%2BwpqvpYAkDhezpGMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=77ea0da9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mobilesuica.com/</a>  , 用你Suica 個email 同password 去login.  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住揀再發行登錄.  你整完係唔會即刻再add 得番張卡. <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imageshack.com/a/img923/3724/aLHxPR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimageshack.com%2Fa%2Fimg923%2F3724%2FaLHxPR.jpg&h=ea59529c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要等到第2朝5am.跟住係iphone 開wallet 個app.  只要你login 左你apple id 係你手機, 應該就見得番你張Suica 卡可以add 番落你手機到."},{"pid":"05e4e5ec68cc564507dde937c73935cee68e7408","tid":460388,"uid":27751,"like":0,"dislike